ELECTRICAL SAFETY DISCLAIMER
=============================
This project involves working with mains voltage (120V AC or higher) which 
can cause serious injury or death if handled improperly. By using, building, 
or modifying this project you acknowledge that:

- Working with mains voltage is inherently dangerous
- This project is provided for educational and personal use only
- The author(s) are not responsible for any injury, death, property damage,
  or other harm resulting from the use or misuse of this project
- This design has not been tested or certified by any safety organization
  (UL, ETL, CE, etc.)
- You should consult a licensed electrician before attempting any mains
  voltage wiring
- Local electrical codes and regulations must be followed
- This project should never be left unattended during initial testing
- Children should never have access to any mains voltage components

If you are not comfortable working with mains voltage DO NOT attempt 
to build this project.

